import "./App.css"
import Header from "./common/header/Header"
import {BrowserRouter as Router, Link, Route, Switch, useParams} from 'react-router-dom'
function App() {
    return(
        <>
        <Header />
        <Router>
        <Switch>
        <Route path="/about">
          <About />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/contact">
          <Contact />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/projects/:id" children={<Project />} />
      </Switch>
    </Router>
       </>
    )
}

export default App
